&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;111&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Compassionate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;client-focused&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;33

&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;110&quot;&gt;🐾&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3&quot; data-end=&quot;104&quot;&gt;Registered Veterinary Technician – Join Our Amazing Team in &lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Woodland Park&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/strong&gt; 🏔️&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;112&quot; data-end=&quot;286&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about exceptional patient care and client education? Do you love the idea of working where mountain views meet wagging tails? If so, we’d love to meet you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;288&quot; data-end=&quot;613&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;308&quot; data-end=&quot;379&quot;&gt;friendly, energetic, and organized Registered Veterinary Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing team in beautiful Divide, Colorado. Nestled in the heart of the Rockies, Divide offers small-town charm, fresh mountain air, and endless outdoor adventure — the perfect backdrop for a fulfilling veterinary career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;288&quot; data-end=&quot;613&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a RVT who can work 4 days out of the week with FULL TIME HOURS - I know how great is that?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WE ARE RELOCATING 8 MINUTES FROM COLORADO SPRINGS IN WOODLAND PARK (JULY 2026)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;620&quot; data-end=&quot;640&quot;&gt;🐶 About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;642&quot; data-end=&quot;680&quot;&gt;As an RVT -vital part of our team-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;642&quot; data-end=&quot;680&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;819&quot; data-end=&quot;1561&quot;&gt;✨ Providing compassionate, thorough client communication and education&lt;br data-start=&quot;889&quot; data-end=&quot;892&quot;&gt;✨ Performing patient assessments and obtaining medical histories&lt;br data-start=&quot;956&quot; data-end=&quot;959&quot;&gt;✨ Assisting in examinations and surgical procedures&lt;br data-start=&quot;1010&quot; data-end=&quot;1013&quot;&gt;✨ Administering and monitoring anesthesia&lt;br data-start=&quot;1054&quot; data-end=&quot;1057&quot;&gt;✨ Placing IV catheters and performing venipuncture&lt;br data-start=&quot;1107&quot; data-end=&quot;1110&quot;&gt;✨ Performing and assisting in laser therapy and acupuncture&amp;nbsp;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1145&quot; data-end=&quot;1148&quot;&gt;✨ Performing radiographs, laboratory procedures and diagnostic testing&lt;br data-start=&quot;1205&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;✨ Administering medications and treatments as prescribed&lt;br data-start=&quot;1264&quot; data-end=&quot;1267&quot;&gt;✨ Implementing treatment plans recommended by our veterinarians&lt;br data-start=&quot;1330&quot; data-end=&quot;1333&quot;&gt;✨ Monitoring hospitalized patients and maintaining detailed medical records&lt;br data-start=&quot;1408&quot; data-end=&quot;1411&quot;&gt;✨ Collaborating with the veterinary team to ensure consistent, high-quality patient care&lt;br data-start=&quot;1499&quot; data-end=&quot;1502&quot;&gt;✨ Supporting smooth and efficient daily clinic operations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1563&quot; data-end=&quot;1670&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you thrive in a dynamic setting filled with lovable pets and dedicated pet parents, you’ll fit right in!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;1100&quot; data-end=&quot;1120&quot;&gt;🎓 What You Bring&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1122&quot; data-end=&quot;1528&quot;&gt;✔ Completion of an accredited Veterinary Technician program (Associate Degree)&lt;br data-start=&quot;1200&quot; data-end=&quot;1203&quot;&gt;✔ Successful completion of the VTNE and eligibility for licensure&lt;br

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Veterinary Assistant Position Available!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about delivering exceptional patient care and educating clients? We are seeking a friendly, energetic, and organized Registered Veterinary Technician to join our team and enhance our commitment to expert care and supportive client relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WE ARE RELOCATING 8 MINUTES FROM COLORADO SPRINGS IN WOODLAND PARK (JULY 2026)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;104&quot; data-end=&quot;122&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;104&quot; data-end=&quot;122&quot;&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;124&quot; data-end=&quot;254&quot;&gt;Join our squad and help us keep tails wagging and pets thriving 🐾 As a Veterinary Assistant, you’ll be a key part of the team by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;256&quot; data-end=&quot;844&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18lw4r&quot; data-start=&quot;256&quot; data-end=&quot;352&quot;&gt;Keeping client communication clear, kind, and actually helpful (no confusing vet jargon here).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;39eh1d&quot; data-start=&quot;353&quot; data-end=&quot;431&quot;&gt;Educating pet parents so they feel confident about their pet’s care at home.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s8mmrm&quot; data-start=&quot;432&quot; data-end=&quot;511&quot;&gt;Assisting with exams, treatments, and procedures alongside our veterinarians.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;v2xs4e&quot; data-start=&quot;512&quot; data-end=&quot;577&quot;&gt;Safely handling and comforting pets (yes, even the spicy ones).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ogse9&quot; data-start=&quot;578&quot; data-end=&quot;639&quot;&gt;Monitoring patient behavior, appetite, and overall vibes 👀&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1tnz5kb&quot; data-start=&quot;640&quot; data-end=&quot;703&quot;&gt;Helping with meds, vaccines, lab work, and basic diagnostics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1hht3px&quot; data-start=&quot;704&quot; data-end=&quot;776&quot;&gt;Keeping things clean, stocked, and running smoothly behind the scenes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;132xxzw&quot; data-start=&quot;777&quot; data-end=&quot;844&quot;&gt;Jumping in wherever needed—because teamwork makes the dream work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;1012&quot;&gt;If you love a fast-paced environment, don’t mind a little chaos (the cute kind), and want to make a real difference for animals and their humans, you’ll fit right in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1019&quot; data-end=&quot;1038&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1019&quot; data-end=&quot;1038&quot;&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1040&quot; data-end=&quot;1498&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;twn4xv&quot; data-start=&quot;1040&quot; data-end=&quot;1104&quot;&gt;You genuinely care about animals and the people who love them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kfkxdo&quot; data-start=&quot;1105&quot; data-end=&quot;1184&quot;&gt;Strong communication skills—you can talk to anyone without making it awkward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;q2xht5&quot; data-start=&quot;1185&quot; data-end=&quot;1247&quot;&gt;Positive attitude and good energy (we’re big on team vibes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;kc5q4h&quot; data-start=&quot;1248&quot; data-end=&quot;1295&quot;&gt;Previous vet clinic experience is a big plus (at least 2 years of experience)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;h6017h&quot; data-start=&quot;1296&quot; data-end=&quot;1365&quot;&gt;You’re a team player but can also handle your own responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;pekr0f&quot; data-start=&quot;1366&quot; data-end=&quot;1423&quot;&gt;Able to multitask and stay organized—even on busy days.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1v6ubhd&quot; data-start=&quot;142
